        <h1 class="font-serif font-black text-white text-4xl sm:text-5xl leading-tight">Sri Lanka's Most Spectacular Waterfalls: A Complete Guide</h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-white/70 text-sm mt-4">
          <span>March 2026</span>
